<body>
<p>Reports incorrect elements in Bean Validation <code>&lt;validation-config&gt;</code> files:</p>

<ul>
  <li>References to non-instantiable classes</li>
  <li>References to classes that do not extend required class</li>
  <li>References to classes with inappropriate scope</li>
  <li>Empty tag and attribute values</li>
  <li>Tag and attribute values that do not match the required pattern (for example, Java Identifiers)</li>
  <li>Tags that do not include required children tags or attributes</li>
  <li>Tags that define objects with duplicate names</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>
<pre><code>
&lt;validation-config&gt;
  &lt;default-provider&gt;<strong>foo.UnknownProvider</strong>&lt;/default-provider&gt;  &lt;!-- Cannot resolve class or package 'UnknownProvider'  --&gt;
  &lt;message-interpolator&gt;my.Interpolator&lt;/message-interpolator&gt;
  &lt;constraint-mapping&gt;META-INF/ConstraintMappings.xml&lt;/constraint-mapping&gt;
  &lt;constraint-mapping&gt;META-INF/<strong>unknown.xml</strong>&lt;/constraint-mapping&gt;
&lt;/validation-config&gt;
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>